Franklin.Lewisburg Avenue Historic District:
Lewisburg Avenue Historic District is a 28-acre (11 ha) historic district in Franklin, Tennessee that was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1988 .
It includes Late 19th and 20th Century Revivals, Bungalow/Craftsman, and Late Victorian architecture.
When listed, the district included 34 contributing buildings and three contributing structures.
